'''特留斯·杨戴尔·纳什'''（{{lang|en|Terius Youngdell Nash}}），生于1981年6月14日，知名于其艺名'''The-Dream'''，是美国的[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]、[[流行乐|流行乐]]创作型歌手、唱片制作人。生于[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[羅京安縣_(北卡羅萊納州)|罗金厄姆]]，由其母雷瓦·纳什（Reva Nash）抚养长大，直至她35岁去世。The-Dream搬到[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]，由外祖父继续抚养。

2001年，The-Dream同拉尼·斯图尔特（Laney Stewart）会面，后者帮助The-Dream拿到了一份发行合同。2007年，The-Dream携手打造了[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]的热门歌曲《Umbrella》以及[[碧昂丝|碧昂丝]]的《Single Ladies (Put a Ring on It)》，这使得他的音乐生涯飞黄腾达。同年，他和[[Def_Jam唱片公司|Def Jam唱片公司]]签约，并与当年晚些时候发布首张专辑《Love Hate》。<ref name="thepopculturejunkie.com">{{cite web |url=http://thepopculturejunkie.blogspot.com/2007/09/what-dreams-are-made-of.html |title=What Dreams are Made of |publisher=The Pop Culture Junkie |date=2007-09-03 |accessdate=2008-09-18 |archive-date=2012-04-29 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67HIyGzCB?url=http://thepopculturejunkie.blogspot.com/2007/09/what-dreams-are-made-of.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年3月，他发行了第二张专辑《Love vs. Money》。<ref name=tracklisting>[http://www.rap-up.com/2009/01/30/the-dream-love-vs-money-album-listening/ The-Dream 'Love vs. Money' Album Listening.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2009/01/30/the-dream-love-vs-money-album-listening/ |date=20090606004458 }} ''Rap-Up.'.' Retrieved January 30, 2009.</ref>2010年6月，第三张专辑《Love King》面世。<ref name="Billboard">{{cite web|url=http://www.bet.com/Music/news/musicnews_thedreamslastalbum_7.29.09.htm|title=The-Dream Reveals "Love King" As His Last LP, But Not Through Twitter|publisher=BET|date=2009|accessdate=2009|archive-date=2012-04-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67HJ4bD8M?url=http://www.bet.com/news/music.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/news/the-dream-announces-love-king-will-be-last-1003997150.story#/news/the-dream-announces-love-king-will-be-last-1003997150.story/ |title=The-Dream Announces "Love King" Will Be Last Album |publisher=Billboard |date=2009 |accessdate=2009 |archive-date=2012-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105115342/http://www.billboard.com/news/the-dream-announces-love-king-will-be-last-1003997150.story#/news/the-dream-announces-love-king-will-be-last-1003997150.story/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

